{"tid":566660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講到法西斯  陳雲法西斯過共產黨、希特拉","createTime":"2018-02-20T06:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T06:46:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe7bef44a58aaa7a77efc9328780d99a05509c6","tid":566660,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:43:18.000Z","msg":"講到法西斯<br />\n<br />\n陳雲法西斯過共產黨、希特拉<br />\n<br />\n我只是呼籲熱血回應淘寶爭議，就被陳雲直接打為偽獨間諜敵人<br />\n<br />\n香港人容不下垃圾，但陳雲容不下善意呼籲<br />\n<br />\n聽其言更要觀其行，陳雲是政治騙子，連內部支持者也敢欺騙，此等人，有何面目今日說人法西斯？？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/144315_4623d4e9881b0309212d9094625e738b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F144315_4623d4e9881b0309212d9094625e738b.png&h=4a5b120a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d088bc1513fb7f6598a3998da42fab300a01936f","tid":566660,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2001563860102649&amp;id=100007471637943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2001563860102649%26id%3D100007471637943&d=BIV5xndJp99C8eXOj408iL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ec9bcac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2001563860102649&amp;id=100007471637943</a>"},{"pid":"e4bc08a2749cec57ad433dc9e69bf5fd417513d0","tid":566660,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"好心唔好再幫依條友宣傳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條友根本就未食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c356b392367ea0603705f245d8e105abb7ca95","tid":566660,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c